snippet.title: LIFE simulators | Brand Reveal
snippet.description:
Have you ever wonder what your life would be like if you could reinvent yourself every day?

Discover NACON’s new brand, the LIFE simulators!

In our LIFE simulator games, you will experience the life of a professional, such as a surgeon, award-winning chef or a train driver, through varied gameplay that combines planning, managing and performing specific tasks related to the relevant profession.
-------------------------------
For news about our other games and products, you can also follow us on: 

Facebook ► https://www.facebook.com/NaconGaming
Instagram ► https://www.instagram.com/NaconGaming
Twitter ►https://twitter.com/Nacon"
